OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain will
OL,6,Fmove southeastwards across the country
OL,7,Fthrough tonight, turning heavy in the
OL,8,Fnorth and west and accompanied by some
OL,9,Frather gusty winds. Showers following
OL,10,Facross Scotland and Northern Ireland
OL,11,Fwhere it will also turn fresher.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FRain will continue to move
OL,14,Facross southern and eastern England,
OL,15,Fagain turning heavy at times. Brighter
OL,16,Felsewhere, with a mixture of sunny
OL,17,Fspells and scattered showers. Feeling
OL,18,Frather fresh.
